  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Welfare of children left behind by female inmates</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">We take care of the babies born to women in incarceration including children left children behind. Sometimes the children left behind are stigmatized, abused and neglected. We ensure these children attend school, eat regularly, get medical help and live in favorable conditions. Vulnerable children will be reported to the Child Welfare Service. In extreme cases the children will be extracted and placed in our facility or another facility awarded by the state.</narrative>
  </description>
